s, VEVs, branching rules, character tables, matrix\n(p,q)_{SU(3)}-representations, Kronecker products, etc. for the groups\ndiscussed above.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Oct 2011 20:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Nov 2011 21:04:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
